data.description: This home combines functionality, style, and comfort. A gorgeous layout that places the main living areas on the lower level and the bedrooms on the upper floor. Throughout the home, you'll find a tasteful and versatile neutral paint palette that graciously accommodates any decorating style you have in mind, ensuring that you can easily make this space your own. The family room is spacious but also designed for your comfort, featuring a lighted ceiling fan. Back door leads to the backyard, creating a harmonious blend of indoor and outdoor living spaces. The eat-in kitchen is complete with a suite of stainless steel matching appliances. The 3-door refrigerator is as practical as it is elegant, while recessed lighting adds a touch of sophistication. A pantry provides ample storage, and the crisp white cabinets. Adjacent to the kitchen, a dining area offers a perfect space for casual meals, ensuring that this area is not only beautiful but also highly functional. For added convenience, there is a half bath on the lower level to accommodate your guests. The laundry room, conveniently located on the lower level, leads directly to the spacious 2-car garage. Upstairs, the second level of this home is dedicated to rest and relaxation, with four well-appointed bedrooms, living area and two full bathrooms. One of the standout features is the versatile den/nursery/game area, measuring an ample 16x12 square feet. playroom, a home office, additional living space. The possibilities are endless. The master bedroom is a true retreat, boasting a lighted ceiling fan, tray ceilings, and a massive 12x10 walk-in closet that provides abundant storage space for your wardrobe and personal items. The en-suite bathroom is equally impressive, featuring double vanities for convenience, a soaking tub to unwind in, and a stand-up shower for those busy mornings. The three additional bedrooms on this level are spacious 2 have walk in closets. Minutes to NAS, NFCU, Beach
